From /mnt/share/bhaskar/rcc_data_extend(already setup,see pipeline)
do the following to link all relevant files.
:
	cd  /mnt/share/bhaskar/rcc_data_extend

	cd rcc
	bash link_pure
	bash link_filter
	bash link_special
	cd ..

Here link_pure, link_filter, and link_special are provided.

Then from /mnt/share/bhaskar/rcc_data_extend directory
python make_dataset_6k.py will setup 6k directory. 
You should already prepared 6k directory and test train valid directories under it.
make_dataset_6k.py is provded here.
